OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FCloudy this
OL,6,Fevening and overnight, with outbreaks
OL,7,Fof rain possible across the south of
OL,8,Fthe region. Becoming somewhat drier
OL,9,Flater in the night, with some clear
OL,10,Fbreaks developing here and there. A
OL,11,Ffew mist or fog patches may also
OL,12,Fdevelop.
OL,13,
OL,14,CSaturday:FThere will still be a lot of
OL,15,Fcloud around on Saturday with
OL,16,Foutbreaks of mostly light and patchy
OL,17,Fdrizzle developing from the south
OL,18,Flater. Feeling a little milder.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
